Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.85,0:01:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.05,0:01:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想買張厚窗簾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.69,0:01:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，得先來整理整理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.01,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚撿到一台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.08,0:02:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#02ちぃ，出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長得這麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又會幫我做各種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是幸福極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打電動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路購物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交友網站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，色情網站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了做這些事\N我一定要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.06,0:03:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一大早就在妄想些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，本須和兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬來沒幾天就帶女孩子回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還蠻厲害的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.31,0:03:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠻厲害的嘛，蠻厲害的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不是這樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看清楚一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都像是電腦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她真是一台\N非常可愛的電腦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你昨天藏的是這女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.61,0:03:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來找你去洗澡時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在想說你是不是\N在藏著什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又沒什麼好藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確，說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.78,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不是說你沒有電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能免費撿到這樣的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能說你的運氣真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，          而且還超可愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我也覺得很幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦能拿來做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿來做什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上上網之類的\N或是做些有的沒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上網的話\N把這裡的接頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她除了“ちぃ”以外什麼都不會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想說她會不會是壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我對電腦一竅不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我用一下那邊的顯示器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？顯示器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.90,0:04:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螢幕啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指電視啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.30,0:04:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示器附有RGB的類比輸入端子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.74,0:05:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示器就會顯示出預設規格\NOS版本以及CPU的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.88,0:05:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是\N新保那傢伙到底在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，顯示出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No          Data是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現No          Data時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.03,0:05:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是資料消失了\N或是還沒安裝軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有安裝OS跟其他軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還會動呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個叫OS的玩意\N就不會動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，OS，作業系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒裝軟體的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦也只不過是個假人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是得去買軟體嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個很貴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.76,0:05:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.72,0:05:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是究竟該安裝\N哪個版本的OS才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，可以稍微讓我弄一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄？你要弄哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.87,0:05:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩是哪家公司的產品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是PCN的\N這裡應該會有型  號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.81,0:06:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹嘛？我在找型  號啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣真的能搞得定電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.99,0:06:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方只不過是台電腦罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當…當然沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.79,0:06:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓絲茉茉來檢查看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把她跟這女孩連線起來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！她掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.13,0:07:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的攜帶式電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉她掛了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.64,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉她壞掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.77,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情好像變得很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.82,0:07:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能去找\N新保介紹的那個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.72,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他家就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用走的就可以到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.92,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的“自製機”是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的這種外貌我從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CPU的速度也快得離譜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是由某人自己拼裝出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己拼裝的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼裝電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這方面的事\N那傢伙知道得非常多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自製機啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安，本須和先生，電腦小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，衣服是不是大了點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我昨晚才剛撿到的\N還沒給她買衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是因為抱著下流的念頭\N才讓她穿上男裝的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…\N如果不介意穿我的舊衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我去拿來給她穿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.05,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你們回來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請到我房間來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那我們先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.77,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的衣物大概也很貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷的舊衣服，這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說日比谷她\N曾經穿過那些衣服對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.85,0:09:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要給這女孩\N是要給電腦穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這地圖看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在這附近沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心中突然燃起了一股無名火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.48,0:09:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是在公開的炫耀\N“我就是有錢人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.99,0:09:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好，這裡是國分寺宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我叫本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問稔先生在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久候多時了，請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.49,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要對電腦流鼻血好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和秀樹先生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是國分寺稔，請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新…新保說要介紹個\N很懂自製機電腦的傢伙給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.68,0:10:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道就是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是個年紀更大的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站著說話也不太方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.82,0:10:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招待他一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招待？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要看到我家的電腦就硬起來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，別弄髒就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個妳不必模仿啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩就是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.76,0:11:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保說的那台\N製造廠商不明的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說沒裝OS還能動，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說只是稍微\N檢查一下而已嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.95,0:11:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛馬影視\N要分析這女孩\N這些電腦的性能還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大型  電腦四台還不夠嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要讓我來試試看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫本須和秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面，本須和少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳是國分寺的姊姊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.38,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我是稔少爺所製作的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.92,0:12:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您想了解她的性能不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.39,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是她發出來的聲音嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料有一部份損毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪個部份的資料？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家事資料以及股票情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是人格資料吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒壞掉吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有造成任何影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心她會壞掉是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且她原本就好像沒裝\N那個叫OS的玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.07,0:13:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確的說法是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和少爺的電腦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連是否有安裝OS都無法確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.85,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法確認？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，她被安裝了防火牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防火牆是什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺已經幫我調整好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，資料好像受損了不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為存有備份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要重新安裝就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有損失極小部份的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒有，沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子，有可能是“Chobits”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亦可稱為傳說中的電腦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在網路上流傳的\N類似都市傳說的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.44,0:15:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說有個以“Chobits”為代號\N進行開發的系列電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦不是很多人在開發嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺你自己不是也在做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我稔就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂“Chobits”是指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透過本身的思考而行動的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.86,0:15:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？柚姬不也是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛她也是主動出面幫忙檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬只不過是\N照著我的程式運作罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我所安裝的程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是正確的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要如何做\N才能以最高的效率完成它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.91,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是經由編輯運算後而執行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然，她也安裝了自動學習程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，她那看似自由的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是得依賴學習程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會發生故障或停止運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有程式就不會動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是Chobits系列則不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來這女孩是台\N很厲害的電腦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想這應該只是謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎？\N畢竟這種都市傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.87,0:16:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著人的外貌卻又非人的物體\N能夠依照感情自由行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是從很久以前就有的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不同嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.39,0:16:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位的外型  \N跟現今各廠牌的電腦都不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來是自製機嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.87,0:16:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再調查看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看有沒有人知道\N關於這女孩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在自製機的BBS站上\N留言問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，BBS是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你的郵件信箱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.55,0:16:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給我吧，給你我的號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.72,0:16:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看有沒有可以寫的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴柚姬就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.56,0:17:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,03-68828-52DF3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記錄完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.68,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，你問她一下電話號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別管那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳知道我的電話號碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.99,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,03-68828-52DF3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說話了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次講出“ちぃ”以外的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.83,0:17:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有安裝學習軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.14,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是被丟在垃圾堆裡，對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是在被丟掉前初始化了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣\N但學習機能卻還留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果好好教她\N我想她不但能夠說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.31,0:17:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠做其他事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你好好教她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她現在的主人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.52,0:18:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會按 照你教她的方式行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我教的方式…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來，不用買軟體也行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不買不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.03,0:18:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.03,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不確定她能安裝哪種軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓她再學習更多的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會自己告訴你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.61,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請下次再來坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假使這孩子學會了說話\N學會了做各種不同的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使她再怎麼乖巧\N再怎麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勸你還是別喜歡上她比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.11,0:18:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想在日後\N傷心流淚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方可是電腦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.54,0:19:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會喜歡上她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可愛到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要我教她\N不過該怎麼做才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望可以合她的身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，非常謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會給您帶來困擾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.61,0:20:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上來換穿看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.29,0:20:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然在我面前脫了起來，我會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把頭轉到那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.64,0:21:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好適合妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.11,0:21:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是究竟要教她什麼\N要怎樣教她呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.45,0:21:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.45,0:21:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保跟國分寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有幫自己的電腦取名字對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.13,0:21:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.03,0:21:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先得教妳自己的名字才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.73,0:21:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.11,0:21:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的名字就叫“ちぃ”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.42,0:21:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我沒辦法好好教妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.62,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過以後請多多指教，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.36,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.03,0:22:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得去幫她買件內褲才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.27,0:22:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.55,0:22:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.63,0:22:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.33,0:22:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.74,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒          感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.48,0:22:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison d'etre像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.15,0:23:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison d'etre如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.49,0:23:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.33,0:23:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.20,0:23:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.41,0:23:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.98,0:23:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.90,0:23:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，當有人要出門時要說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.17,0:23:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.20,0:23:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.14,0:23:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.37,0:23:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.37,0:23:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是水壺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.47,0:23:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.01,0:23:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水壺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.54,0:23:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.18,0:23:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是矮腳餐桌\N秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.78,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.48,0:23:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.28,0:23:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.05,0:23:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.28,0:24:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits下一回\N「ちぃ，記得了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.49,0:24:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明有這麼多秀樹在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.25,0:24:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賺生活費的秀樹\N卻只有我一個嗎？